data.description: Discover country living in this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with breathtaking views across 2.6 acres. Step inside to find a vaulted great room that captures the open concept living. In the heart of the home the large picture windows bring the outside in. The family room also has a wood burning fireplace to cozy up to. If you love the outdoors, the acreage offers endless possibilities. Recent blacktop driveway added and a refreshed deck.
